      "message": "There is a generic mechanism to prefix plugin metrics, see https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/Documentation/dev-plugins.html#_providing_own_metrics.\n\nThough it seems this doesn\u0027t work for plugin contributed queue metrics, I guess `WorkQueue` could be enhanced to support this prefixing. The plugin name would need to be passed to another `createQueue()` method so that WorkQueue can read the config option `plugin.\u003cplugin name\u003e.metricsPrefix`. I think that\u0027s beyond the scope of this change and could be done in another change. So for now I would document the behavior in the plugin config documentation.",
